{"type": "article", "id": 29578, "title": "像素拼图", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-13T23:09:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607132106413KSd9MtGV2wpjWI8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>要在拼图上玩出花样，或许没有比像素风更合适的了。来自韩国的 <a href=\"http://www.mavcdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">mavcdesign</a> 最近同像素艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.joojaebum.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jaebum Joo</a> 联手打造了一套 8-bit 风格的拼图 PIXU，分为自画像和名画两种款式：Joo 会根据你提供的照片绘制出像素头像，再由 mavcdesign 制作出相应的拼图；名画系列则包含了《星空》、《呐喊》、《蒙娜丽莎》等六幅画作的迷你拼图。虽然 PIXU 的成品并不大，但这种独特的风格搭配个性化的定制实在是种草能力十足。值得一提的是，自画像更是限量 550 人。如果你对这个拼图感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mavcdesign/pixu-on-demand-brick-pixel-portrait\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，自画像款和名画款的早鸟价分别为 24 和 44 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713212523Lmvjeyps8WQViflJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651563\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 317px; width: 375px; left: 396px; top: 696px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713212524JidyeKn61YPNIsE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713212523BFlN5i7C2kDrypSm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713212523fiZKRYpejzH9huSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}